Package: taxFun
Version: 0.99.0
Date: 2022-04-26
Title: taxFun
Authors@R: c(
    person("Vinh", "Tran", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "tran@bio.uni-frankfurt.de"))
Description: taxFun provides a set of functions for working with NCBI taxonomy. For example, the user can convert between taxon IDs, scientific names and the taxonomy ranks. He/she can create taxnomy tree from a list of taxon IDs or taxon names. One can also sort the taxa based on their taxonomic distance; etc.
URL: https://github.com/trvinh/taxFun/
BugReports: https://github.com/trvinh/taxFun/issues
